WEBVTT

00:01:58.000 --> 00:02:03.176
because the Board of Education in fact
would send a teacher to my house.

00:02:03.200 --> 00:02:05.016
And they did

00:02:05.040 --> 00:02:08.735
for a total of two and a half hours

00:02:08.759 --> 00:02:09.976
a week.

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:11.256
(Audience murmurs)

00:02:11.280 --> 00:02:13.336
But for good behavior,

00:02:13.360 --> 00:02:16.376
they threw in an occupational therapist

00:02:16.400 --> 00:02:19.256
who taught me that very essential skill

00:02:19.280 --> 00:02:20.720
of cross-stitching.

00:02:21.280 --> 00:02:22.536
(Laughter)

00:02:22.560 --> 00:02:23.896
I don't cross-stitch today.

00:02:23.920 --> 00:02:26.296
(Laughter)

00:02:26.320 --> 00:02:30.016
I didn't actually get to go to school
in a real building